        "TileImage": "$($repository dab94294-69b8-472f-9a05-cb474b9a671f).Image",
        "Description": "Hello 47,\rYour next targets are three senior risk management officers of a New York bank, whose analysis and predictions came into conflict with the profit goals of the bank most recently.\rDue to how heavily the financial system is regulated, and how strong positions the employees hold within the bank, there is no legal way for the general assembly to get them out of the way, or overlook their recommendations. Hence the contract.\rI will leave you to prepare.",
